he dialects of [[Orcs]] and other evil beings.<ref>{{LR|Lhammas}}</ref>\n\nThough it seems this concept was later dropped by Tolkien, in the late text labelled ''[[Ósanwe-kenta]]'' it was mentioned that Melkor indeed had developed a language for those who served him by the time of the [[War of the Powers]], as [[Manwë]] himself told the [[Eldar]].<ref>{{NM|Osanwe}}, p. 213</ref>\n\n{{references}}\n{{languages}}\n[[Category:Valarin]]"}}}